{
  "book": 20,
  "chapter": 28,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The wicked flee when no one pursues, but the righteous are bold as a lion. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wicked flee when no one pursues, but the righteous are bold as a lion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When a land transgresses, it has many rulers, but with a man of understanding and knowledge, its stability will long continue. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When a land transgresses, it has many rulers, but with a man of understanding and knowledge, its stability will long continue."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "A poor man who oppresses the poor is a beating rain that leaves no food. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "A poor man who oppresses the poor is a beating rain that leaves no food."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
