          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Whoever robs his father or his mother and says, “That is no transgression,” is a companion to a man who destroys. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Whoever robs his father or his mother and says, “That is no transgression,” is a companion to a man who destroys."
